title: Dark Charizard 21/82 Team Rocket Regular ~ First Edition NM
description: The product is a vintage Dark Charizard Pokémon card from the Team Rocket set, part of the first edition release. This rare collectible features Charizard, a Dragon-type Pokémon, with 80 HP and is in English language. Illustrated by Ken Sugimori, this Stage 2 Pokémon card is manufactured by The Pokémon Company in the United States. It is a standard-sized card made of card stock with a regular finish, making it a valuable addition to any Pokémon TCG collection.
